<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Flag_of_Hong_Kong&action=edit&section=5.php.html" title="Edit section: Colour specifications">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Colour_specifications">Colour specifications</span></h3>
